### Phase 2: Huginn Tasks Enhancements

Based on the feature requests in requirements.md:

| Feature | Effort |
|---|---|
| Make table content selectable (copy-paste) | Small — remove `user-select: none` on table, add it only on drag interactions |
| Popup edit modal for single task | Medium — new modal component |
| Bulk edit popup (hotkey `E`) | Medium — reuse modal with restricted fields |
| Mail icon → open `mailto:` with task details | Small |
| CSV export of current filtered view | Small — already has CSV export, adapt to use filtered set |
| Toggle reduced/full columns | Small — column visibility toggle |
| Dedicated "overdue/due" filter button | Small |
| State logic review (new→started→done→stopped + derived states) | Medium — requires `startedAt` timestamp, new status values |

