### Phase 3: Huginn Cal Overhaul

Requirements call for substantial changes:

| Feature | Effort |
|---|---|
| Show tasks/projects from Tasks & Plan data | Medium — read from shared JSON |
| Multi-day events with labels | Large — new data model for events (vs current day→status map) |
| Paintbrush hotkey editing (already partially done) | Small polish |
| Non-contiguous day selection + batch assign/remove | Medium |
| 4 visualization views (compact list, weekly table, monthly table, aligned monthly) | Large — 4 new render functions |
| Week/month number filters | Medium |
| CSV export of current view | Small |
| `.ics` email export | Medium |

#### Files

- **[MODIFY] `experimental/huginn cal` (new version)** → substantial rewrite with new event data model

---

### Phase 4: Huginn Plan (New Component)

This is the most complex piece. Key subsystems:

1. **Project hierarchy tree** — infinite depth, with auto-created start/end milestones and default task
2. **Tree view UI** — expand/collapse, inline edit, hotkeys, layer filtering, full-text search
3. **Dependency management** — visual dependency arrows, constraint types (flexible/fixed/target dates)
4. **Scheduler** — critical path calculation, conflict detection, constraint resolution
5. **Gantt chart view** — synchronized with tree view, collapsible, dependency arrows, critical path highlighting, available-window visualization
6. **Conversions** — task↔project, group→project
7. **Auto-creation** of "personal tasks" L1 project from Huginn Tasks data

#### Files

- **[NEW] `experimental/huginn plan v1.0.html`**

---

### Phase 5: Huginn Timekeeper Updates

Adapt to use the shared data model:

- Use tasks/projects from shared JSON instead of its own project tree
- Remove ability to create new projects (per requirements)
- Keep all visualization and editing features

#### Files

- **[MODIFY] [experimental/huginn timekeeper v0.1.html](file:///Users/yurybodrov/Documents/huginn/experimental/huginn%20timekeeper%20v0.1.html)** → bump version

